Thinly slice the @tomato{2}.

Tear the @sliced Irish ham{80%g} into pieces.

Just before serving toss the @salad leaves{40%g} with a drizzle of @oil{to taste} 
and half the @balsamic glaze{2%sachets}.

Season to taste with @salt{to taste} and @pepper{to taste}.

Divide the tomato slices between plates.

Place a handful of dressed salad leaves in the middle of each plate and place a 
whole ball of @mozzarella{250%g} on top of the salad.

Drizzle over the @green pesto{30%g} and remaining balsamic glaze.

Crack some pepper on top.